{"id": 2692, "genre": 1001, "title": "你发现在哪些体验中，保持体面的努力总是徒劳的？", "description": "做完彩超后的医生。扔了两张纸巾给你：“自己擦干净，穿好衣服，走！”宛如一个渣男。——饭否·钢板樱桃（题图来自：iStock ©️ Doloves）", "record_count": 2958, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181225110917zwnuEUhMLakR3BTK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-26T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 318976, "content": "遇到坏人对自己侵害的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541905}, {"id": 318977, "content": "在大冬天，保持体面总是徒劳的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541912}, {"id": 319233, "content": "想跟爸妈聊一聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1519313}, {"id": 318978, "content": "三个人的友谊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541920}, {"id": 318979, "content": "让一个人认同你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053886}, {"id": 318980, "content": "刚刚从初中进入高中，刚刚从高中进入大学，想要表现的更好，不过最后还是依旧我行我素，过着没有朋友的生活，习惯了一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1437951}, {"id": 318981, "content": "吵架！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541929}, {"id": 319243, "content": "在大场合演讲或发言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522014}, {"id": 318990, "content": "和一条路走到死的人论理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1512910}, {"id": 318992, "content": "去政府机关办事，如果你不懂条文，被公务员踢来踢去是正常的，一股无名火，心想如果能有差评都好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244165}, {"id": 321297, "content": "跟蛮不讲理的人讲理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551602}, {"id": 319507, "content": "写文案", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544002}, {"id": 318998, "content": "被要出电梯的人扒拉", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "s